"title": "5884: indecision",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5884: indecision",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Uncertainty, hesitation and doubt reflect a failure of the basic human ability to choose. They reveal an internal debate and lack of conviction.</p>\n<h2>Indecision arising from doubt and hesitation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:6-Jas1:8\">JAS 1:6–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">MAT 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:21\">MAT 21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23\">MRK 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:23\">ROM 14:23</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of indecisive behaviour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:11\">EXO 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:13\">EXO 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:10-Exod14:15\">EXO 14:10–14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:10\">JOS 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:8\">EST 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:21-Matt27:26\">MAT 27:21–27:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:9-Mark15:15\">MRK 15:9–15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:13-Luke23:25\">LUK 23:13–23:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:38-John18:40\">JHN 18:38–18:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:11-Mark16:14\">MRK 16:11–16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:25\">JHN 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:25\">ACT 24:25</a></p>\n<h2>Indecision may be indicative of divided loyalty</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:22\">MAT 19:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22\">MRK 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:23\">LUK 18:23</a></p>\n<h2>Indecision or uncertainty may be prompted by Satan</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1\">GEN 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:4\">GEN 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a></p>",
